(nextExecutionDate, isEnabled. 12.2 Sync Flow User saves income or expense. FinanceRepository) Tj
T*
(inserts the transaction into Room. A background coroutine attempts to upload the transaction) Tj
T*
(to Firestore. If Firestore succeeds, the local row is marked isSynced = true. If network) Tj
