(21. Conclusion FinPilot is designed as a scenario-specific personal finance app for Ka) Tj
T*
/F1 10 Tf
(Silva. It focuses on the problems that caused previous tools to fail: multi-source income,) Tj
T*
(invisible discretionary spending, low tolerance for manual entry, and a savings goal that) Tj
T*
(was not connected to everyday behaviour. The implementation uses a modern Android stack:) Tj
T*
(Kotlin, Jetpack Compose, Navigation Compose, MVVM, StateFlow, Coroutines, Firebase) Tj
T*
(Authentication, Firestore, Room, Retrofit, WorkManager, and Koin. The architecture separates) Tj
T*
(UI, ViewModels, repositories, and data sources while supporting offline-first transaction) Tj
T*
(capture and background cloud sync. The system therefore meets the main technical constraints) Tj
T*
(of the SE3092 assignment and provides a credible product that could improve Kavindu's) Tj
T*
(financial clarity within the first week of use. End of Technical Design Document) Tj
T*
